ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of RICHARD DeLAND FRENCH of Montréal, Quebec, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designate RICHARD DeLAND FRENCH to be Vice-Cahirperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission; effective February 28, 2005.
